<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Y2K-MAIN-0102-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Y2K FEARS SUBSIDE, BUT TRUE TEST MAY COME MONDAY
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By MARILYN GEEWAX
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
