<P>
   More than 1,000 photographs depicting the 20th century.
</P>
<P>
   16.(x) FAITH OF MY FATHERS, by John McCain with Mark Salter.
</P>
<P>
   (Random House, $25.) The U.S. senator and former POW
</P>
<P>
   recalls his life and the lives of his father
</P>
<P>
   and grandfather in the Navy. (b)
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ADVICE, HOW-TO AND MISCELLANEOUS &LR;
</P>
<P>
   1. GUINNESS WORLD RECORDS 2000. (Guinness, $25.95.)
</P>
<P>
   A profusely illustrated collection of records about
</P>
<P>
   subjects as various as sports and technology.
</P>
<P>
   2. EVERY DAY'S A PARTY, by Emeril Lagasse with Marcelle
</P>
<P>
   Bienvenu and Felicia Willett. (Morrow, $26.) Recipes
</P>
<P>
   for cooking Louisiana style.
</P>
